SmProcessing

Class RawTraceConversion

  • java.lang.Object
    • SmProcessing.RawTraceConversion

  • public class RawTraceConversion
extends java.lang.Object
    This static factory class is used during processing of raw trace counts to physical values. No object instantiation is used, just call the factory methods with class name and method name, such as RawTraceConversion.countToG(). Use this class to convert counts to either units of g or cm/sq.sec.
